&lt;p&gt;We are seeking experienced Account Executives with a proven track record in B2B SaaS sales. Array provides an industry-leading suite of consumer credit solutions designed to strengthen financial relationships between institutions and their customers. We are particularly interested in AEs with experience selling to financial institutions and fintechs to drive growth and deliver tailored solutions for their needs.&lt;/p&gt;
