&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain relationships with clients, serving as the face of the company and promoting growth through strategic sales activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consult with prospective clients to understand their needs and recommend products or services that align with their business goals, particularly in credit services and debt settlement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research and analyze prospect companies, markets, and client needs to create tailored sales discussions that demonstrate the value of Array’s solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present compelling sales proposals that showcase Array’s industry-leading suite of consumer credit solutions to potential banking and credit union clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attend trade association meetings and industry conferences to build networks, identify opportunities, and represent Array as a leader in consumer credit solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel to meet clients or to attend conferences; expect to travel once a month.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a habit of using AI tools to think, build, and ship faster—it’s your default, not an afterthought.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You Have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
